\pard\f0\fs28 Small, glabrous, somewhat fleshy herbs with opposite, exstipulate cauline leaves. Flowers in terminal cymes. Stamens 3. Ovary superior; ovules 3. Fruit a globose capsule dehiscing with 3 valves. Seeds broadly reniform, black.
\par

\par

